Package org.anchoranalysis.core.progress

Classes to allow for tracking the progress of a task that can be broken into smaller units, for reporting to the user.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CheckedProgressingSupplier<R,E extends Exception>
    Like CheckedSupplier but can update a progress-reporter as the operation progresses.
    Progress
    Tracks the completion of an operation, as divided into sub-units of progress.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CachedProgressingSupplier<T,E extends Exception>
    Memoizes (caches) a call to CheckedProgressingSupplier
    ProgressConsole
    Displays the current progress to the console.
    ProgressIgnore
    Placeholder that doesn't measure any progress.
    ProgressIncrement  
    ProgressMultiple
    Combines a number of sub progress reporters.
    ProgressOneOfMany  
    TraversalResult  
    TraverseDirectoryForProgress
